# Session 16 Handover тАФ Fumage

## What was done this session

### New article тАФ So You Want to Make Your Own Cologne (`/guide/diy-cologne`)
DIY perfumery and bespoke fragrance services guide. Five-section structure: (1) The Premise тАФ lede with drop cap, pull quote on the critic-vs-kitchen gap; (2) The Reality Check тАФ five numbered failure modes (materials cost, formulation as discipline, stability, IFRA compliance, dilution math) plus a Cost of Entry callout ($600тАУ$1,800+ entry); (3) The Path Forward тАФ four practical principles (course/text first, reputable suppliers, accord as unit of work, meticulous records) plus chord/symphony pull quote; (4) Bespoke Services тАФ six dark service cards (Imaginary Authors, Scentbird/Commodity, Olfactive Studio, Ffern, Scent Trunk, Your Local Perfumer); (5) Practical Framework тАФ five principles (reference library, aggressive constraint, skin testing, resist adding, maceration time) plus Minimum Viable Brief callout; (6) The Honest Comparison тАФ four-route dot-rating matrix (Full DIY, Online Service, Independent Perfumer, Established House) across Quality Ceiling, Effort Required, and Cost. Registered under "The Craft ┬╖ DIY & Bespoke". Commit `8612886`.

