## Design constants (carry forward)

- Background: `#0c0906` ┬╖ Body: `stone-200` ┬╖ Accent: `amber-500`/`amber-400`
- Labels: `text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]` ┬╖ Card border: `border-stone-800`, hover `border-stone-600`
- Aesthetic: apothecary-editorial тАФ dark, warm, not sterile e-commerce
- Guide articles: `font-serif` display/body, `max-w-2xl` container, pull quotes via left amber border
- Guide article components (`PullQuote`, `SectionLabel`, `FragLinks`, `FragCard`) are defined inline per file тАФ intentionally not shared
- Nav order: Catalog ┬╖ Houses ┬╖ Notes ┬╖ Dupes ┬╖ Guide ┬╖ Search ┬╖ Wardrobe/Sign in
- Commits: imperative subject line, Co-Authored-By trailer
- Fragrance slugs: always verify against `prisma/data/fragrance_database.json` using the `id` field before referencing in guide articles тАФ never invent a slug, render unmatched as plain text
- Mobile nav: hamburger handled by `MobileNav.tsx` (client component); desktop nav is `hidden md:flex` in `Nav.tsx`
- Source HTML files for articles come from `~/Downloads/` тАФ convert to TSX faithfully, adapting to the Fumage dark design system
- Session-close sequence (mandatory): (1) `npx tsc --noEmit`, (2) `git push`, (3) write handover, (4) update project-fumage.md memory entry
